### Quick Commerce API Flow
### Run in order: Search -> Get Product -> Place Order -> Replay (idempotency)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Search Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/products?product_name=Lays
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get Product By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/products/prod-001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Place Order (Buy Now)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: order-test-001

{
    "user_id": "user-001",
    "product_id": "prod-001",
    "quantity": 1,
    "amount": 2000,
    "metadata": "123 Main St, Bangalore",
    "latitude": "12.9716",
    "longitude": "77.5946"
}

###

### 4. Replay Same Order (Idempotency Test - should return same order)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: order-test-001

{
    "user_id": "user-001",
    "product_id": "prod-001",
    "quantity": 1,
    "amount": 2000,
    "metadata": "123 Main St, Bangalore",
    "latitude": "12.9716",
    "longitude": "77.5946"
}

###

### 5. Out of Stock Test (order large quantity)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: order-test-oos-001

{
    "user_id": "user-001",
    "product_id": "prod-001",
    "quantity": 9999,
    "amount": 19998000,
    "metadata": "Test address",
    "latitude": "12.97",
    "longitude": "77.59"
}

###

### 6. Missing Idempotency Key (should 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": "user-001",
    "product_id": "prod-001",
    "quantity": 1,
    "amount": 2000
}

###

### 7. Inactive User (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: order-test-inactive-001

{
    "user_id": "user-003",
    "product_id": "prod-001",
    "quantity": 1,
    "amount": 2000
}
